title: Battle Frenzy
description: A sky with two moons; a soul world of endless possibilities;Lonely darkness, and a strange and mysterious clown!A federation of 100 cities. Three great empires. A world where monsters run rampant.This is an age where heroes are born, where humanity strives to retake the earth!And at the epicenter of it all: a special second-year student, Wang Zhong, who uses the power of the Playful Roulette to shake the whole world! You hear that, ladies? Your Senior is here!
